in our own lifetime.

69
00:07:44,465 --> 00:07:46,698
"But," he said,

70
00:07:46,800 --> 00:07:49,868
"let us begin."

71
00:07:51,572 --> 00:07:53,438
Today,

72
00:07:53,540 --> 00:07:57,409
I'd say to all
my fellow Americans,

73
00:07:57,511 --> 00:08:00,512
"Let us continue."

74
00:08:07,321 --> 00:08:10,522
We have talked
long enough

75
00:08:10,624 --> 00:08:13,959
in this country
about civil rights.

76
00:08:14,061 --> 00:08:19,397
We have talked
for 100 years or more.

77
00:08:19,500 --> 00:08:23,935
It is time now to write the
next chapter in the books of law.

78
00:08:25,939 --> 00:08:27,939
I urge you to enact

79
00:08:28,041 --> 00:08:32,777
President Kennedy's
civil rights bill into law

80
00:08:32,880 --> 00:08:35,947
