00:11:32,793 --> 00:11:34,059
and the rest
of those liberals

139
00:11:34,161 --> 00:11:35,694
a little bit of red meat
now and again.

140
00:11:35,796 --> 00:11:38,630
- Yes, but- - Sir, Dr. Martin
Luther King is on three.

141
00:11:38,732 --> 00:11:41,266
Well, he can wait.

142
00:11:44,705 --> 00:11:48,773
So last night was just, uh,
election year politics or not?

143
00:11:48,875 --> 00:11:50,508
Absolutely.

144
00:11:50,610 --> 00:11:54,079
But I need you to hold the
South for me, Uncle Dick.

145
00:11:54,181 --> 00:11:57,782
Party unity, it is gonna be critical.

146
00:11:57,884 --> 00:11:59,984
Well, we can
talk more about it

147
