for Christ's sake.

186
00:13:45,225 --> 00:13:47,892
Not another one of these
scrawny, old Washington biddies.

187
00:13:47,994 --> 00:13:49,794
Oh, God damn it, Manny.

188
00:13:49,896 --> 00:13:52,397
Don't you have anything that doesn't
make me look like a dago undertaker?

189
00:13:52,499 --> 00:13:55,700
I wanna thank you,
Dr. King,

190
00:13:55,802 --> 00:13:57,669
for your public
expression of support.

191
