00:54:26,163 --> 00:54:28,163
and the country
goes up in flames.

983
00:54:28,266 --> 00:54:31,433
Now, we're making
history here, Everett,

984
00:54:31,535 --> 00:54:32,901
and you have to decide

985
00:54:33,004 --> 00:54:36,372
how you want history
to remember you-

986
00:54:36,474 --> 00:54:39,041
as a great man,

987
00:54:39,143 --> 00:54:42,745
a man who changed
the course of this country,

988
00:54:42,847 --> 00:54:47,816
or somebody who just likes
to hear himself talk.

989
00:54:49,020 --> 00:54:50,319
Congress is not alone

990
00:54:50,421 --> 00:54:52,454
in contributing problems
