to get him back home, Robert.

999
00:55:11,275 --> 00:55:13,575
We'll talk more about
this business in Tonkin.

1000
00:55:13,678 --> 00:55:16,545
- Yes, sir.
- And, Walter, anything that McNamara needs,

1001
00:55:16,647 --> 00:55:18,247
- you make sure he gets it.
- Yes, sir.

1002
00:55:18,349 --> 00:55:19,882
- Is Humphrey still around?
- Hey, Daddy!

1003
00:55:19,984 --> 00:55:22,017
Hey, now, don't-
don't just run off.

1004
00:55:22,119 --> 00:55:24,086
- Come give me a hug.
