It's all right, boys. I think
I'm safe with Senator Fulbright.

1035
00:56:33,858 --> 00:56:35,324
I'll see you up on three.

1036
00:56:35,426 --> 00:56:37,159
Boy, oh, boy,
look at you.

1037
