This is the seal of the
presidency of the United States.

1061
00:57:33,584 --> 00:57:36,819
There's only two cuff links
like this in the entire world

1062
00:57:36,921 --> 00:57:39,087
and you now
own them both.

1063
00:57:39,190 --> 00:57:41,089
I want you to wear them
in good health, Bill.

1064
00:57:41,192 --> 00:57:43,325
And think about
what I said, huh?

1065
00:57:43,427 --> 00:57:46,728
You look good, Bill. I bet
you dropped a few pounds, huh?

1066
00:57:46,831 --> 00:57:50,399
I'm gonna need another set
of those cuff links.

1067
00:57:50,501 --> 00:57:53,135
What the hell?

1068
00:57:53,237 --> 00:57:54,837
Walter.

