1076
00:58:12,723 --> 00:58:15,390
If he's conscious,
he can vote!

1077
00:58:15,493 --> 00:58:17,392
...but I know my Bible.

1078
00:58:17,495 --> 00:58:20,829
And the Bible does not say that
we cannot choose our own neighbor.

1079
00:58:20,931 --> 00:58:23,599
The Bible does not say
that we cannot build a wall

1080
00:58:23,701 --> 00:58:26,101
betwixt ourselves
and our neighbor.

1081
00:58:26,203 --> 00:58:30,239
Johnson: What I need is some
help on this cloture vote.

1082
00:58:30,341 --> 00:58:32,274
No? Well,
I'll tell you

1083
00:58:32,376 --> 00:58:34,209
what protects
a small state, Alan,

1084
00:58:34,311 --> 00:58:36,478
and it damn sure
isn't a filibuster rule.

1085
00:58:36,580 --> 00:58:39,748
It's a strong president
who's in your corner.

1086
00:58:41,385 --> 00:58:42,851
What- now where-

1087
00:58:42,953 --> 00:58:45,854
where on Earth
do you get that-

1088
00:58:45,956 --> 00:58:48,891
well, I don't forget
these things.

1089
00:58:48,993 --> 00:58:50,392
You understand me?

1090
00:58:50,494 --> 00:58:52,160
Son of a bitch.

1091
00:58:52,263 --> 00:58:53,729
I thought I had him.

1092
00:58:53,831 --> 00:58:55,697
Now, for a man
named Bible,

1093
00:58:55,799 --> 00:58:58,400
he sure doesn't have a handle
on the New Testament.

1094
00:58:58,502 --> 00:59:00,736
This bill will guarantee

1095
00:59:00,838 --> 00:59:05,040
the commercial destruction
of white people everywhere!

1096
00:59:05,142 --> 00:59:06,909
Senator Cannon,

1097
00:59:07,011 --> 00:59:08,744
listen,
Carl Hayden and I

1098
00:59:08,846 --> 00:59:12,080
are finally putting together the
Central Arizona Water Project.

1099
00:59:12,182 --> 00:59:15,150
And if Nevada wants
any part of this,

1100
00:59:15,252 --> 00:59:17,319
I need your vote.

1101
00:59:17,421 --> 00:59:18,921
Yes, yes, yes,

1102
00:59:19,023 --> 00:59:21,123
I know how Alan Bible
feels about it,

1103
00:59:21,225 --> 00:59:22,591
but I'm talking
to you now,

1104
00:59:22,693 --> 00:59:25,794
combat veteran
to combat veteran.

1105
00:59:25,896 --> 00:59:27,930
Yeah.

1106
00:59:28,032 --> 00:59:31,266
Yeah, it is
a big damn decision,

1107
00:59:31,368 --> 00:59:34,369
but Democrats have
to stick together here.

1108
00:59:36,774 --> 00:59:39,041
Listen- no, now-
no, Howard, just-

1109
00:59:39,143 --> 00:59:41,276
Howard, listen to me,
