ahead of us here.

1113
00:59:49,353 --> 00:59:52,554
You know I'm gonna be
there for you when it counts

1114
00:59:52,656 --> 00:59:56,558
and can I count
on you now?

1115
01:00:00,564 --> 01:00:02,898
Howard, you do
the right thing here

1116
01:00:03,000 --> 01:00:04,800
and you're gonna
help yourself

1117
01:00:04,902 --> 01:00:07,336
and you're gonna help
your state

1118
01:00:07,438 --> 01:00:09,805
and you're gonna help
your country.

1119
01:00:10,574 --> 01:00:13,041
Will you vote
for cloture?

1120
01:00:19,283 --> 01:00:21,350
Howard,
you're a good man.

1121
01:00:21,452 --> 01:00:23,151
Thank you!
Bye-bye.

1122
01:00:23,253 --> 01:00:26,421
- 67 votes!
- Congratulations.

1123
01:00:26,523 --> 01:00:29,825
Should we let Senator Dirksen
make the public announcement?

1124
01:00:29,927 --> 01:00:32,361
You think there's any way
we can stop him?

1125
01:00:36,433 --> 01:00:39,067
Johnson:
<i>We believe all men</i>

1126
01:00:39,169 --> 01:00:43,739
<i>are entitled</i>
<i>to the blessings of liberty.</i>

1127
01:00:43,841 --> 01:00:46,041
<i>Yet millions</i>

1128
01:00:46,143 --> 01:00:50,112
<i>are deprived</i>
<i>of those blessings,</i>

1129
01:00:50,214 --> 01:00:54,549
not because
of their own failures,

1130
01:00:54,652 --> 01:00:58,920
but because of the color
of their skin.

1131
01:01:00,290 --> 01:01:03,392
<i>This cannot continue.</i>

1132
01:01:03,494 --> 01:01:06,928
Our Constitution
forbids it.

1133
01:01:07,031 --> 01:01:10,565
The principles
of freedom forbid it.

1134
01:01:10,668 --> 01:01:15,671
And the law I will now sign forbids it.

1135
01:01:15,773 --> 01:01:17,639
Thank you

1136
01:01:17,741 --> 01:01:20,876
and good day.

1137
01:01:30,220 --> 01:01:32,320
Man:
<i>Reverend King.</i>

1138
01:01:34,091 --> 01:01:37,225
Humphrey: We did it. We did it.

1139
01:01:37,327 --> 01:01:38,760
