I'm not feeling sad
tonight, Dr. King.

1502
01:21:54,410 --> 01:21:56,610
I'm not feeling
forgiveness.

1503
01:21:56,712 --> 01:21:58,846
Woman:
<i>Preach.</i>

1504
01:21:58,948 --> 01:22:01,548
