to feel angry with me.

1506
01:22:05,521 --> 01:22:07,354
- Congregation: Yes.
- Are you angry?

1507
01:22:07,456 --> 01:22:12,126
- Yes!
- The white men who murdered James Chaney

1508
01:22:12,228 --> 01:22:13,594
are never
gonna be punished.

1509
01:22:13,696 --> 01:22:15,496
Congregation:
<i>That's right.</i>

1510
01:22:15,598 --> 01:22:20,634
The best way
to remember James Chaney

1511
01:22:20,736 --> 01:22:23,704
is to demand our rights.

1512
01:22:23,806 --> 01:22:25,572
If you go back home
and take

1513
01:22:25,675 --> 01:22:29,209
what these white men
are doing to us...

1514
01:22:30,913 --> 01:22:34,682
