your souls!

1516
01:22:36,919 --> 01:22:39,086
<i> Stand up!</i>

1517
01:22:40,423 --> 01:22:42,756
We got to stand up
in Meridian!

1518
01:22:42,858 --> 01:22:46,226
- Congregation: Yeah!
- We got to stand up in Jackson!

1519
01:22:46,329 --> 01:22:47,561
Congregation:
Stand up!

1520
01:22:47,663 --> 01:22:49,396
And when we get
to Atlantic City,

1521
01:22:49,498 --> 01:22:52,199
