- Stand up!
- Stand up!

1525
01:22:58,240 --> 01:22:59,873
Stand up! Stand up!

1526
01:22:59,976 --> 01:23:01,742
Stand up! Stand up!

1527
01:23:01,844 --> 01:23:03,711
Stand up!
Stand up!

1528
01:23:03,813 --> 01:23:07,414
<i>One man, one vote!</i>
<i>One man, one vote!</i>

1529
01:23:12,588 --> 01:23:14,221
