1531
01:23:17,860 --> 01:23:21,428
Now, you don't understand the
depth of feeling among my people.

1532
01:23:21,530 --> 01:23:24,365
These murders, they've
rocked the movement.

1533
01:23:24,467 --> 01:23:27,868
If the government does not
do what is right here,

1534
01:23:27,970 --> 01:23:30,771
nonviolence will no longer
be an option.

1535
