<i>appear here</i>

1537
01:23:39,148 --> 01:23:41,181
<i>claiming to be</i>
<i>an alternative delegation.</i>

1538
01:23:41,283 --> 01:23:44,451
It's something I don't think has
happened in the Democratic Convention

1539
